{"per_page":10,"total":15,"current":14,"data":[{"title":"Linux查找含有某字符串的所有文件","date":"2018-05-15T22:17:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>如果你想在当前目录下 查找”hello,world!”字符串,可以这样:<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -rn &quot;hello,world!&quot; *</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/72","tags":["files","grep","pattern","pattern2","匹配","参数","命令","文件","目录"],"categories":["DataBase"]},{"title":"百度语音demo","date":"2018-05-09T02:07:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>package com.fh.controller.tts;<br></p>","link":"post/64","tags":["error_info","final","import","java","private","string","url2"],"categories":["Java"]},{"title":"apache实现二级域名访问不同项目目录","date":"2018-05-09T01:39:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/62","tags":["p","servername","www","别名","参数","命令","域名","文件","服务器","目录"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":"win7下用xampp部署php项目","date":"2018-05-03T00:15:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h2 id=\"1、下载xampp安装\">1、下载xampp安装<a href=\"post/58#1、下载xampp安装\"></a></h2><p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/2397354493.png\" alt=\"xampp\" class=\"article-img\"><br></p>","link":"post/58","tags":["config","db'","master'","p","php","xampp","数据库","文件","目录"],"categories":["Other"]},{"title":"Tomcat启动成功没有报错，但网页打不开","date":"2018-04-27T02:53:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/55","tags":["his","tomcat","war","webapp","目录"],"categories":["Other"]},{"title":"Mybatis报错org.mybatis.spring.MyBatisSystemException","date":"2018-04-26T00:01:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/54","tags":["error_info","flec","getter","named","nested"],"categories":["Mybatis"]},{"title":"这大概只能是死宅才会体会的快乐吧","date":"2018-04-24T04:20:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/48","categories":["Life"]},{"title":"在本地用navicat链接不上阿里云ECS服务器上的数据库问题解决","date":"2018-04-22T23:16:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"问题原因：mysql权限问题\">问题原因：mysql权限问题<a href=\"post/44#问题原因：mysql权限问题\"></a></h1><h1 id=\"解决方法-1：\">解决方法 1：<a href=\"post/44#解决方法-1：\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">//设置root用户通过123456密码可以从任何主机连接到mysql服务器</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt;GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO &apos;username&apos;@&apos;%&apos; IDENTIFIED BY &apos;password&apos; WITH GRANT OPTION;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.00 sec)  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">//刷新mysql权限表</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt;FLUSH PRIVILEGES;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.00 sec) </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">//查询用户表</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; select host,user from user;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>ALL PRIVILEGES –所有的权限，当然这里也可以写增删查改update delete insert select</li>\n<li><em>.</em>  – 指的是所有数据库的权限，‘<em>数据库.表’</em></li>\n</ul>","link":"post/44","tags":["grant","mysql","privileges","rows","指定","数据库","服务器","权限","访问"],"categories":["DataBase","Liunx"]},{"title":"CentSO 7.4 下安装jdk1.8、mysql、php服务","date":"2018-04-22T22:51:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"1-安装jdk1-8\">1.安装jdk1.8<a href=\"post/43#1-安装jdk1-8\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk\">1.1 安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1.1 安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk<a href=\"post/43#1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk\"></a></h2><p>命令：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa |grep java</span><br><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa |grep jdk</span><br><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa |grep gcj</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>如果没有输入信息表示没有安装。<br>如果安装可以使用如果安装可以使用<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa | grep java | xargs rpm -e --nodeps</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>批量卸载所有带有Java的文件  这句命令的关键字是java</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-2-检索包含java的列表\">1.2 检索包含java的列表<a href=\"post/43#1-2-检索包含java的列表\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum list java*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","link":"post/43","tags":["1.8.0","gcj","grep","java","javarpm","jdkrpm","mysql","open-jdk","php","php-fpm","service","yum","命令","安装","文件","系统"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":"阿里云服务器下(centOS)中安装ftp","date":"2018-04-20T03:17:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"1-安装常用工具和依赖库\">1.安装常用工具和依赖库<a href=\"post/40#1-安装常用工具和依赖库\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo yum install wget axel unzip gcc bison git autoconf nfs-utils pcre-devel zlib-devel bzip2-devel cmake gcc-c++ ncurses-devel perl-Data-Dumper libicu-devel libquadmath-devel python-devel libxml2-devel openssl-devel libcurl-devel libpng-devel freetype-devel freetype-devel gd-devel libmcrypt-devel libxslt-devel libevent-devel systemd-devel make gtk+-devel openssl keyutils patch perl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h1 id=\"2-获取PHP\">2.获取PHP<a href=\"post/40#2-获取PHP\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget http://cn2.php.net/distributions/php-7.1.9.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","link":"post/40","tags":["ftp","ftpservice","permanent","systemctl","tcp","yes","zone","命令","客户端","文件","服务器","端口"],"categories":["Liunx"]}]}